Eon Natty who recently got himself into rebranding in collaboration with his new family M.B Entertainment is set to beat all odds to create as much music as he could.  His new single “For Good” is a smashing new anthem for the new year and his official debut release under the newly signed label. As expected, it is a solid tune we are going to be grooving to nonstop till the end of this year.  The new song is expected to drop on all music platforms on May 21,2021  It is pertinent to note that with his unending passion for music; Eon Natty deserves privilege for a continuous 2021 playlists. 